snippet.title: Horse Racing Manager Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist the game on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2740170/Horse_Racing_Manager/

Horse Racing Manager is an upcoming game whre you build your legacy in the horse racing world. Breed the next champion, making key decisions on training the horse and choosing its diet. Every choice counts, and every race tells a story. Create your own rags-to-riches journey, from being a stablehand to owning the greatest racing stable in the game.
